Billye LEEPER, as Administratrix of the Estate of William V. Lewis, Deceased, v. MARYLAND CASUALTY COMPANY. No. 5745. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. Dec. 9, 1957. Foliart, Hunt & Shepherd, Oklahoma City, Okl., and Stevenson, Huser & Huser, Holdenville, Okl., for appellant. Horsley, Epton & Culp, Wewoka, Okl., for appellee.

Before BRATTON, Chief Judge, and BREITENSTEIN, Circuit Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed on motion of appellant.
